  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\n`altair.processAttestation()` calculates the total balance of the validator set for every index of every attestation.\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2021-06-02 14-47-01](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35266934/120482737-b3512780-c3b1-11eb-90da-2c8eaf931e64.png)\r\n![Screenshot from 2021-06-02 14-47-20](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/35266934/120482749-b5b38180-c3b1-11eb-86ac-a805b6ab6c92.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nThis part should be optimized, and compute that total balance the least number of times possible.\r\n",
